race.comment: HAPPY CHICK (3) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by one length (16.78) at this track. Looks well placed and should be tough to beat. MR. OTTO (4) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing third and beaten 1.5 lengths (16.88) behind HAPPY CHICK at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Hard to beat again. ACE IS FIRE (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Little Jack Finn (16.74) in a Grade 5. Expected to feature. BOROUGH COOK (2) can measure up with the right run.
